results.code:
Client ->> MW: HTTP request
 MW ->> Auth: Seed corrId / tenant / device in CLS
 Auth ->> Guards: Attach req.user on success
 Guards ->> Int: Enforce session + device + RBAC
 Int ->> Ctrl: Optional Tx + set_config(app.*)
 Ctrl ->> Svc: Call application service
 Svc ->> Repo: Use repository port
 Repo ->> Prisma: Query via ContextService.db()
 Prisma ->> DB: SQL
 DB -->> Prisma: Rows
 Prisma -->> Repo: Model
 Repo -->> Svc: Domain object
 Svc -->> Ctrl: DTO / domain
 Ctrl -->> Client: JSON response
